reviewText: All of your maternal instincts will come to life at these ultra cute kittens. Rush to your nearest animal shelter and adopt one or two today!

I don't see how a DVD of kittens could get any better.  The video quality is very good and the photographer does a great job when the kittens start bouncing off the walls.

The only reason I didn't give this 5 stars is that the 8 scenes each have a different pure breed of kitten and and they don't have any normal looking kittens.

Other than that this is a fun video and unique.
